         <div type="comments">
            <p><note type="parallels"><ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a266"/> (completing); MaitrHami 16, 13-15; MaitrSiŋgim, Taf. 161, 162, 51</note><note type="philcomment">This fragment, which complements <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a266"/>, contains part of the sixteenth act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka. Uy. parallels are MaitrHami 16, 13b20-15a2, and MaitrSiŋgim, Taf. 161, 162, 51 (<bibl><title corresp="ref:tekin1980"/><citedRange>139-143</citedRange></bibl>). Immediately follows <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a286"/>+<ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a260"/>. See also <bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1999"/><citedRange>202-203</citedRange></bibl>.</note><note type="remarks">Fragment of a manuscript which includes A 251 - A 294 (cf. <bibl><title corresp="ref:gengetal2004a"/><citedRange>64-65</citedRange></bibl>).</note></p>
